     <td valign=top width=470>                                                              


      <center>
      <table border=0 cellpadding=3 cellspacing=0 width=475>
	    <tr>
         <td style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10pt;" background="/images/bg_heading_blue_01.jpg"><center><b>Continent to Continent</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
		 <td>                            
	                                   

	    <table border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0>
		  <tr><td><font color="00dd00">Submitted by:</td><td><font color="00dd00">Keaian Wolvespaw</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Event Date:</td><td>08/05/2000</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Start Time:</td><td>6:00 PM EST</td></tr>
      <tr><td>End Time:</td><td>??</td></tr>
        </table>
	  <br>
	  <br>


          I didn't get a chance to post before Azure Sky did.  So be that as it may, Order of Balance was planning on hosting a naked gnome race from Akanon to Halas on June 29th.  So not to interfere with Azure Sky I have changed our date till Aug 5th.  Our race will be alot different then what you may be used to.<br>
          <br>
          This will not be a individual race event.  Teams will be formed and objectives set from zone to zone.  <br>
          <br>
          1.  All participants will turn their tome into the PoD.  Thus becoming a PVP.  <br>
          (outside help at this point will be useless for PVP players fall under different rules then regular players) <br>
          <br>
          2.  Teams will form before the race begins.  Each team will chose one member as prime leader for their team.  The prime leader for the team will then be entered into the guild and responsible for his/her teams actions.  Thus the prime leaders will make all anouncements to their team.  <br>
          <br>
          3.  Designated zones will be labeled Ambush zones.  This means that other teams may try to take out the competition by killing them and sending them back to akanon to start over.   <br>
          <br>
          4.  Supplies will be given out before the race to the prime leader of each team.  It will be his/her responsibility to ration it out to the team.  Supplies may include, food, water, spells, potions, etc...  that will help aid the team along the way.  <br>
          <br>
          5.  Other zones will have items that the team will need to loot in order for their team to win the race.  (example.. aviak chick talon, skunk gland.. etc.. )  These items will be turned in at the end of the race by the Team Leader.  <br>
          <br>
          6.  Q:  How to win?<br>
              A:  Get your entire team to the zone inside Halas first.  Turn in items that were requested. Bang.. You win<br>
          <br>
          This race will not be a simple lets see who can get their first type of race.  It was conceived as a team event.  Monitors will be set in certain zones.  All participants will not be permitted to be /anon or /role.  <br>
          <br>
          A small entry fee of 10pp will apply.  This will be used to help get some supplies and the remainder will be added on to the plat prize at the end of the race.  All members of the winning team must be present at the finish line for their team to be announced the victor.      <br>
          <br>
          If you wish to sign up for this event or have queastions about it please visit our <a href="http://pub17.ezboard.com/forderofbalancegeneral.showMessage?topicID=10.topic">message board</a> and make a reply so that I may tally the amount of people going to attend.  If attendance is low the event will not take place:(.  Hope to see ya there<br>
          <br>
          Keaian<br>
          <br>
          </td>
		 </tr>
		</table>

		
		
